@chapulina I am actually testing it on a system that allows me to "reset" the environment and on a normal install. Both aren't working even after trying to uninstall everything. Here are the commands I am doing on the clean version every time:
```
apt update
apt install -y libjansson-dev libboost-dev imagemagick libtinyxml-dev mercurial cmake build-essential wget nodejs npm nodejs-legacy
npm install -g grunt

curl -ssL http://get.gazebosim.org | sh

cd ~; hg clone #!/osrf/gzweb
cd gzweb/
hg up default

curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/creationix/nvm/v0.33.0/install.sh | bash
export NVM_DIR="$HOME/.nvm"
[ -s "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh" ] && \. "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh"
[ -s "$NVM_DIR/bash_completion" ] && \. "$NVM_DIR/bash_completion"

npm run deploy
```
